{"tid":698828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社發英文評論 強調中國解決朝核問題有貢獻","createTime":"2018-06-12T04:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T06:59:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"05d6975d3009bb2071294472faf16b18782f3b26","tid":698828,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180612/large/1528775374_a37e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180612%2Flarge%2F1528775374_a37e.jpg&h=bc78bfc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普與北韓領導人金正恩，今日在新加坡舉行歷史性會面，中國官方新華社在會面開始後發表英文評論，指這次會晤燃起解決朝鮮半島永久和平的希望，本身具有歷史性意義，有望描繪出無核化道路，也預示着半島揭開了和平與繁榮的新篇章。<br />\n<br />\n文章又稱，目前極待解決的一個問題，是通過恰當地照顧到各方關切，將當前來之不易的緩和轉變為朝鮮半島的持久和平。文章強調，中國在解決朝鮮半島問題上的貢獻：中國提出的雙軌制方案，己被證明是切實可行的合理解決方案，中國將繼續作出貢獻，在推動和平解決半島核問題方面發揮建設性作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58307742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58307742&d=2lwlGKa7mSP44RAh4nKyUgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=7b319ee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58307742&h=280e82df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58307742</a>"},{"pid":"ceebde479e18478b03617601ff5808317c35ca85","tid":698828,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a910c2093270ce99520c26e43036a74332ab69a1","tid":698828,"uid":16567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"咁樣磨爛蓆法真係好樣衰"},{"pid":"1da516c205a13017fd264e70f965065fa6cd1241","tid":698828,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.es